Speaker 1: Your call has been forwarded to an automated voice messaging system.

Speaker 2: Alfred Masioka.

Speaker 1: Is not available.

Speaker 2: At the tone, please record your message. When you finish recording, you may hang up or press one for more options.

Speaker 1: To leave a callback number, press five.

Speaker 2: Hey Alfred, this is Nick. Just got your voicemail and returning your call.

Speaker 1: Feel free to call me back.

Speaker 2: Uh... I was just on the other line at that time.

Speaker 1: Thank you so much. Bye bye.
